Title: Spin Structures on Kleinian Manifolds

Comments: 8 pages

TopologyJournal-ref: Class.Quant.Grav. 11 (1994) 2411-2416

We derive the topological obstruction to spin-Klein cobordism. This resulthas implications for signature change in general relativity, and for the $N=2$superstring.